CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 11, 1953, pg. 12 reads: "Easter Bonnet Parade...held at the home of Mrs. Mary Clark, Easter Sunday as the annual feature of Achievement Club No. 8 Easter tea, showed these fair ladies as winners: Mrs. Deloris Harris, Mrs. Alis Nelson and Miss Maria Henderson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Deloris Harris, Alis Nelson, and Maria Henderson, posing for Easter bonnet parade in home of Mary Clark, for Achievement Club No. 8 Easter tea
